UPDATE `posts` SET `id` = 31,`user_id` = 5,`title` = 'Small Business and Why',`slug` = 'small-business-and-why',`content` = 'Some facts of small business turn out not to be so small after all. In the United States small businesses are said to represent <I><B><U>99.7% of all employers</U></B></I>. They <I><U>pay 45% of all private payrolls </U></I>as well. While nearly half of the payroll they account for half of the private sector employees as well.&nbsp;Also just about <I><U>53% of small business are home based</U></I>, and home run. Why is this important you ask? Its important that somebody had a dream and followed their dream to take a path less taken. Our world as we know it is made up of huge banks, big box stores and large corporations. Small business requires lots of hard work and dedication. There is no shortage of competition out there and gaining trust in your business is paramount for success. So&nbsp;next time you&nbsp;need some paint, think about&nbsp;going to the local Joes hardware instead of Home Depot. Or next time your family&nbsp;goes out for a meal, concider Aunt Millies Home Cook''n instead of greasballs fast food. Small business may not always be the cheapest decision available but a thank you and a handshake can bridge that gap quite quickly. The small guy depends on you for his sucess, and&nbsp;he will work harder to make your dollar go a little bit further&nbsp;then the others.&nbsp;Keep us around, give us a try. Buy local and support small business.',`meta_title` = '',`meta_description` = '',`meta_keywords` = 'russ',`created_at` = '2013-06-09 01:39:29',`updated_at` = '2013-06-09 08:56:42',`image` = 'russ/logo.png' WHERE `posts`.`id` = 31;
